snippet.title: TasteMaker trailer
snippet.description:
Add TasteMaker to your wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1289340/TasteMaker_Restaurant_simulator/

TasteMaker gives you the opportunity to build and manage your own restaurant. Design the interior and exterior, decorate, create a menu, manage staff and more. You will need to keep your guests satisfied to prevent the restaurant of your dreams from turning into the restaurant of your nightmares.
